      <title>Zelenskiy说，向美国投资核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/zelenskiy-says-open-to-us-investing-in-ukraine-s-nuclear-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Volodymyr Zelenskiy排除了对乌克兰核电站的控制权，但在与唐纳德·特朗普的电话打来电话后，释放了美国对他们进行投资的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/zelenskiy-says-open-to-us-investing-in-ukraine-s-nuclear-plants</guid>
